narration_text: #C C is unrolling the foil paper
#C C puts the foil paper on the table
#C C puts fish fillet on the foil paper
#C C puts the small particles of fish off the hand
#C C throws the garbage to the dustbin
#C C pours paste into fish fillet
#C C put the paste in the fridge
#C C puts the fillet in the oven
